  <brief_title>A Pilot Investigation of Ciclesonide When Administered as a Hypotonic Versus an Isotonic Formulation of Ciclesonide Nasal Spray</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pilot Investigation of the Nasal Mucosal Absorption, Retention, and Metabolism of Ciclesonide When Administered as a Hypotonic Versus an Isotonic Formulation of Ciclesonide Nasal Spray When Each Formulation Is Administered to Currently Symptomatic Patients (18 Years or Older) With Documented Perennial Allergic Rhinitis (PAR).</official_title>
