  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to measure the amount of a nasal steroid spray (ciclesonide)
      absorbed by the tissue in the nose 2 hours after having this study drug sprayed in the nose
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
